<lb/> I am desired by the Vice-President to
<lb/>transmit, for the information of His Excellency
<lb/> the Lord Lieutenant, the accompanying statements
 <lb/>as to the movements, &amp;c., between April 22nd
<lb/> and May 1st of all the members of the 
