<lb/> present. Any further statements will be 
<lb/>forwarded as received.</p>


<closer><salute>I am,	
<lb/>Sir, 
<lb/>Your obedient Servant,
<signed>T. P. Gill</signed>
<lb/>Secretary.</salute>

<address><addrLine>The Under Secretary,
Dublin Castle.</addrLine></address>

<add>Chief Commissioner
<date>8/5/16</date></closer></add>
        
    

    
                </body>
            </text>

        
            
        

         

